No output.

    [5]-&gt; Stream.of(1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9).peek(System.out::println).count();
    |  $23 ==&gt; 9

No output.

    [6]-&gt; Arrays.asList(1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9).stream().peek(System.out::println).count();
    |  $25 ==&gt; 9

No output.

    [7]-&gt; IntStream.range(1, 10).filter(i -&gt; true).peek(System.out::println).count();
