Outputs numbers 1 to 9.

    [1]-&gt; List&lt;Integer&gt; list = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();
    |  list ==&gt; []
    [2]-&gt; Stream.of(1, 5, 2, 7, 3, 9, 8, 4, 6).sorted().peek(list::add).count();
